  m_Name: DemonData_Shelldon
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_Shelldon
  demonName: Shelldon
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: '"A shell appears.  Have you done it?  Have you summoned a demon
    goddess of beauty?


    Nope.  It cracks open to reveal two eyes and a sumptuous
    mustache, stands on two little legs and adjusts its tie.


    ""Oh my,"" it
    says in a chipper voice, ""You really should organize your files better.""

    "'
  minimumPowerLevel: 20
  maximumPowerLevel: 25
  outcome: 
  boon: Gain 1 Sanity
  bane: 
  boonBaneDialogue: 
  dateOutcome: '"He''s too short for rock climbing, too small to reach the pedals
    for a bike ride, too small to see the screen while sitting in a movie theater,
    but none of that stops him.  He approaches every date idea with gusto and enthusiasm,
    and tells you he''s been trying to be open to new experiences, even when he doesn''t
    really know how to manage it.


    Honestly, the little dude fills you with
    inspiration."'
